```
Occupation   base   Birth           adj   Family     adj
Ranger       31–34  Only child      +5    Green Elf   0
Archer       41–44  1 of several     0    Grey Elf   +5
Warrior      61–64                        High Elf  +10
Mage         76–79
Prince       91–94
King         96–99
```

